OL,3,CWho is the new owner of Everton FC?
OL,5,FIt is the beginning of a new era for
OL,6,FEverton FC who have been taken over by
OL,7,FAmerican consortium The Friedkin Group
OL,8,F(TFG).
OL,10,FThe deal was sealed on Thursday 19
OL,11,FDecember after TFG CEO Dan Friedkin
OL,12,Fagreed to a deal to purchase Farhad
OL,13,FMoshiri's 94.1% stake in the club.
OL,15,FThe Premier League's statement
OL,16,Fconfirmed TFG had purchased a 98.8%
OL,17,Fstake in Everton.
OL,19,FWho is the man reigning over the
OL,20,FPremier League club?
