OL,3,CWho is the new owner of Everton FC?
OL,5,FSince 2013, the father-of-four has
OL,6,Fbeen chairman of Auberge Resorts
OL,7,FCollection, a range of luxury resorts,
OL,8,Fhotels and vacation properties located
OL,9,Facross North America, Costa Rica,
OL,10,FEurope, the Caribbean, and Fiji.
OL,12,FThe billionaire has had a colourful
OL,13,Fcareer, including working as a
OL,14,Fstuntman in the award-winning film
OL,15,FDunkirk in 2017.
OL,17,FHe piloted a Spitfire fighter plane in
OL,18,Fthe closing scene of the film, which
OL,19,Fhe was given a Taurus Stunt Award for
OL,20,FBest Speciality Stunt.
