OL,3,CWho is the new owner of Everton FC?
OL,5,FFriedkin invested money into Roma's
OL,6,Fplaying squad and has overseen the
OL,7,Fclub winning the 2021-22 UEFA Europa
OL,8,FConference League.
OL,10,FIn a letter addressed to Everton fans,
OL,11,FDan Friedkin said: "I take immense
OL,12,Fpride in welcoming one of England's
OL,13,Fmost historic football clubs to our
OL,14,Fglobal family, The Friedkin Group.
OL,16,F"Everton represents a proud legacy,
OL,17,Fand we are honoured to become
OL,18,Fcustodians of this great institution.
