OL,5,F"The Friedkin Group is a diverse
OL,6,Ffamily of companies with a global
OL,7,Ffootprint spanning industries such as
OL,8,Fsports, automotive, entertainment,
OL,9,Fhospitality, and adventure.
OL,11,F"Across all our endeavours, we strive
OL,12,Fto deliver extraordinary experiences
OL,13,Fthat ignite people's passions. We are
OL,14,Fthrilled to bring this ethos to
OL,15,FEverton and the Liverpool City Region.
OL,17,F"Whilst we are new to the Club, we
OL,18,Ffully understand the vital role
OL,19,FEverton plays in local culture,
OL,20,Fhistory, and the lives of Evertonians
OL,21,Fhere and around the world.
